## Summary
This documentation page explains Profiles in Amplitude, which allow joining customer profile data from data warehouses with behavioral product data, functioning as standalone properties associated with user profiles rather than specific events, and supporting integration with Snowflake, Databricks, and S3 with detailed setup instructions for each platform.

